# JavaScript standards

- HTML/CSS must work without JS
- IIFE or deferred scripts; no global pollution
- Feature detection, not UA sniffing
- Event delegation on stable parents
- Prefer `textContent`, `classList`, `dataset` over `innerHTML`
- Fail silently — guard with early returns
- No frameworks; scripts in `assets/js/`
- Update ARIA state when toggling UI (e.g. `aria-expanded`)
